FLASHCARD APPLICATION

Overview:
This program will give a random question for a specified course pull randomly from a assortment of
questions. It will then give the user the option to either present the answer or go to
the next flashcard. This can be mainly used for studying math/physics to practice setting up
problems.


Features:
Draws from pool of questions with solutions which can be changed at anytime.

Gives randomly selected questions each time prompted.

Can provide solution or just problem.

Can switch between courses for different studying dates.
